  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study, the investigators will study spinal anesthesia for laparoscopic
      cholecystectomy in comparison to general anesthesia (GA) regarding patient satisfaction as a
      primary variable, intraoperative complications, postoperative analgesic requirements,
      postoperative nausea and vomiting, patient hospital stay (secondary variables).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
